{
  "stem": "7739.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I think this was one or one of two occasions where they had given us different coats.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I was given a-- a jacket, which was quite welcome, because I-- my clothes, like everybody else's, was almost in tatters.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And some of the people were using cement bags to line their clothes in the winter time, particularly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We had to walk from camp to work-- I would imagine about two or three kilometers there and two or three kilometers back under-- under guard.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And our shoes were getting worn, and our clothes was getting sprinkled with hot oil from the-- from the-- from the factory.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was given a jacket in-- in which there was a bullet hole in it, or two bullet holes, I forget now.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I found a one pound note in it, sewn in also in this jacket.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this pound note, I was able to go to Auschwitz with it and bribe a kapo there with it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, we were in this camp, Starachowice, and we worked there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two epidemics broke out, where it took a heavy toll of people with typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In our-- In the adjoining camp, on the [INAUDIBLE] camp, the Germans came one day and made a general appell, or roll call.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And those who had typhoid fever-- I don't know whether you know how this-- this sickness evelop-- develops.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You get a fever, And you hit the high of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Either you die, or you start recovering.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The problem was you had to go to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you weren't going to work, you weren't getting enough food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there were no nurses, no doctors, mind you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there was two doctors-- one doctor in camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
